description: Vol 18, No 1 (2013): The Syrian Uprisings: Reflections on the Past Two Years The bulletin is a biannual publication of the Syrian Studies Association. This issue includes feature articles focusing on the past two years of the conflict in Syria. It also includes news of the Syrian Studies Association and book and film reviews.
title: Vol 18, No 1 (2013): The Syrian Uprisings: Reflections on the Past Two Years
